media.description: An object that describes the properties of media that the service supports. notifications.description: The notification configuration for the Service instance. See [Push Notification Configuration](https://www.twilio.com/docs/chat/push-notification-configuration) for more info.

sid.description: The unique string that we created to identify the Service resource.

typing_indicator_timeout.description: How long in seconds after a `started typing` event until clients should assume that user is no longer typing, even if no `ended typing` message was received.  The default is 5 seconds.

url.description: The absolute URL of the Service resource.

webhook_filters.description: The list of webhook events that are enabled for this Service instance. See [Webhook Events](https://www.twilio.com/docs/chat/webhook-events) for more details.

webhook_method.description: The HTTP method to use for calls to the `pre_webhook_url` and `post_webhook_url` webhooks.  Can be: `POST` or `GET` and the default is `POST`. See [Webhook Events](https://www.twilio.com/docs/chat/webhook-events) for more details.
